[Weekly Briefing] Nurburgring Nordschleife - 2016s2 Week 7




[i][b]Welcome to the SRF![/b]
We pride ourselves on a friendly, competitive and yet relaxed atmosphere both on and off-track. Don't be afraid to ask for help, either in practice sessions or on the forum![/i]

[img]http://members.iracing.com/jforum/posts/downloadAttach/2429680.page[/img]
[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Nordschleife Industriefahrten [/b]
Week 7 of 12 - 2016 Season 2[/size][/color]
Race Distance: 3 laps, approximately 25-30 minutes

This week we travel to the famous 'Green Hell' - Nurburgring Nordschleife. This is the touristfarhten layout - i.e. NOT including the GP track. 
[img]https://d3bxz2vegbjddt.cloudfront.net/members/member_images/tracks/nurburgringnordschleife/html/Nord/lib/img/map-nord.svg[/img]
(Right click -> Open Image in New Tab to view bigger)

[size=18][color=red][b]IMPORTANT NOTES THIS WEEK[/b][/color][/size]
	- There will be separate qualifying sessions, not the attached qualifying that we normally have!
	- The track takes a LONG time to load on most PCs - be aware of this and join the race session in plenty of time!
	- We only have 3 laps in the race - survival is paramount because a tow back to the pits will basically end your race. Concentrate on being clean and safe and you will get a good result.

